the Room, my private email on the media. In tonight=E2=80=99s edition, high=
lights from the inaugural month of The Grill Room, my twice-weekly podcast =
in which I sit down with media executives, operators, and talent to discuss=
 all the disruptions, transformations, and sturm und drang across the indus=
